INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('126', '16', '2', '1', '2012-11-16', '<p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">For Project Portfolio project, I had reviewed more documents for Science Permit Application and Tracking System (SPATS).&nbsp; I am reviewing mission need statements and other documents.&nbsp; Mohammad and I will be meeting with business manager to get more understanding about this project.&nbsp; We are waiting for Business manager&rsquo;s time to get the meeting setup.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">For Project Portfolio project, I have continued to work on databases, middleware, Server OS, Web Server, Reporting tools and other tools for the project I am assigned too. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">As for Mission critical business process project, We didn&rsquo;t receive any feedback from the core team regarding initial data summary.&nbsp; Al&rsquo;Tariq had sent out this summary to the field/state offices for their review.&nbsp; Based on this feedback, we may need to re-analyze the data.&nbsp; I will wait until we get more feedback from field/state offices.</span></p>\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Project Portfolio &ndash; Updated a table of databases, middleware, Server OS, Web Server, Reporting tools, other tools, and Geospatial application list.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Project Portfolio &ndash; Started to create a document detailing SPATS project.&nbsp; This document will be useful in meeting with Business manager and for future work on this project.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Mission Critical Process Project &ndash;Summary draft of initial data was sent out to BLM State/Field offices by Mr. Al&rsquo;Tariq Samuels.</span></p>\r\n</p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '2', '4', '2012-11-16 15:45:50', '4', '2012-11-28 15:26:37');
INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('127', '13', '2', '1', '2012-11-16', '<p>Quiet short week. &nbsp;Began updating the IRM SharePoint site to reflect ILM and its changes but only have partial access...can\'t upload, can\'t fully edit pages, and there are other problems with the site (broken links, error messages, etc. &nbsp; Will get with Mike Smith next week to see what can be done to broaden my rights or see if there might be some in-house programming assistance. Edited Roles and Responsibilities page (in HTML, no less) to bring it current with Portfolio Management and other current concepts.</p>', '<p>Completed the first instance of a ConOps for the Project/Portfolio Management Tool Implementation project (to go along with the Mission Needs Statement and Charter turned in previously). &nbsp;The BLM template clearly originated in the military, asks questions about deployment on ships and aircraft. I tailored the ConOps for BLM purposes.</p>\r\n<p>Completed/delivered the FINAL(?) version of the Integrated Lifecycle Management (ILM) framework. Per Ms. Bowers, accepted changes, polished spacing, did a final spelling/grammar check. Final review meeting on Monday with internal team prior to publication.</p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p>N/A</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2', '4', '2012-11-16 16:34:26', '4', '2012-11-28 15:28:25');
INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('128', '18', '12', '1', '2012-11-16', '<p>Received Word document with changes, additions and deletions.</p>', '<p>Making the changes as requested.</p>', '<p>none.</p>', '<p>Lots of the changes were not either in red or had lines with notes attached. From what I can only figure out is that someone did a \"Accept changes\" command, so I\'ve been having to go line by line in the whole word document to see what needs to be changes. This is a MAJOR issue. &nbsp;It was suppose to be the FINALIZED word document, when I received it the first time, with all the changes requested and that I\'ve also found, it\'s at least 40% changed.</p>', '<p>I\'ll talk to Kerry about this matter above on Monday.</p>', '1', '18', '2012-11-16 17:36:38', null, null);
INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('129', '18', '12', '1', '2012-11-23', '<p>Redid the TOC numbering, since 10 more pages were added because of all the additional copy added.</p>\r\n<p>Reviewed the Word document against the Quark document again, looking to make sure I didn\'t miss any changes that were in red and NOT in red. Compared the whole word document to Quark document, to make sure I caught everything I could find, before submitting the PDF for proofing. Did spell check again.</p>', '<p>Submitted PDF for proofing, along with Word document that shows other things that were NOT marked in red from client but were changed by them, so they could see this also.</p>', '<p>none.</p>', '<p>Spoke to Kerry on phone and wrote email on Monday, to advise him of the word document issues.</p>', '<p>none.</p>', '1', '18', '2012-11-20 12:32:34', null, null);
INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('130', '16', '2', '1', '2012-11-23', '<p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\">\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">For Project Portfolio project, I am reviewing mission need statement and other documents.&nbsp; Mohammad and I will be meeting with business manager to get more understating about this project.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Reviewed Project Portfolio presentation from ITIB presented two weeks ago by Al\'Tariq and Sayed.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 12.6pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">For Mission Critical Process project, I had a brief discussion with Al&rsquo;Tariq to find out the feedback from the field offices.&nbsp; So far Al&rsquo;Tariq hasn&rsquo;t heard anything from the field.&nbsp; He will update me whenever he gets feedback.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Project Portfolio &ndash; Started to create a document detailing SPATS project.&nbsp; This document will be useful in meeting with Business manager and for future work on this project.</span></p>\r\n</p>', '<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Attend a WO-570 staff meeting to discuss status of the projects and get update from Al&rsquo;Tariq on current projects/status.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '2', '4', '2012-11-23 15:41:09', '4', '2012-11-28 15:32:15');
INSERT INTO `statusreport` VALUES ('131', '13', '2', '1', '2012-11-23', '<p>Began editing the ILM per directives from the IRT meeting. Subsequent interplay regarding directive to remove references to the Technical Review Board, resulted in replacement of TRB with Information Resources Management Advisory Committee (IRMAC). Spent considerable time trying to locate the IRMAC charter. &nbsp;Does not seem to be on any of the Bureau web sites. Will follow up with inquiry to Directives next week.</p>\r\n<p>Attended BisonConnect training course for Google Guides.</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '<p>IRT meeting to review ILM generated a dozen or so relatively innocuous but useful changes.</p>\r\n<p>FDCCI meeting cancelled.</p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '2', '4', '2012-11-26 09:46:22', '4', '2012-11-28 15:30:08');
